short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Amazon won’t ship to you? We’re here to help!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shipped.io Extension adds "Connect account" button to Amazon.com product pages. Click on the button when browsing Amazon.com to connect your shipped.io account Then simply add products from Amazon directly to your cart with a simple click.

Features:

Quick, Easy, and Reliable delivery service.

-Allows you to add products from Amazon
-Automatically shows you the final price
-Checkout and place your order on shipped.io website
-Fast delivery to your doorstep within 2 weeks

Any questions? We’d love to hear from you: 

-Email us at iraq@shipped.io 

-Check our website “https://iq.shipped.io/pages/how-it-works  ”
